{"tid":1322723,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"五個你要馬上原諒達哥的理由","createTime":"2019-07-16T04:34:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T06:05:32.000Z","uid":251052,"like":15,"dislike":103,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"7185aafae738abed87b5592d23b91b791519db85","tid":1322723,"uid":251052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:34:30.000Z","msg":"1. 言論自由同時代表有保持沈默既自由<br />\n就算達哥咁做係會助長咗打壓言論自由果一邊，我地都唔應該因為咁而成個連衛兵咁逼達哥表態<br />\n<br />\n2. 達哥已經表示關注事件<br />\n達哥係公眾人物，佢唔可以光明正大反政府同支持暴徒，咁會教壞佢班觀眾（大部分係中小學生），況且達哥已經表示對事件高度關注<br />\n<br />\n3. 達哥需要養家<br />\n達哥同大部分香港人一樣要供樓，而且佢仲有咁大間遊戲公司要營運要好多資金，佢因為接政府同馬雲既廣告而噤聲，並唔係因為佢貪錢，而係佢要彌補返個tum呀，達哥只求打個和<br />\n<br />\n算 我都係唔講太多了，真兄弟自然會明白"},{"pid":"32962f8b85d4e5095a94bb188fb95a57d20b11e1","tid":1322723,"uid":50658,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:35:39.000Z","msg":"五個"},{"pid":"da5cd2c038aa3f705e2668c445aa89ea2b07557f","tid":1322723,"uid":25391,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:36:29.000Z","msg":"一直關注事件呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e279366bd5401a6a934b8318d6478d47e239cdbb","tid":1322723,"uid":251052,"like":13,"dislike":5,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"32962f8b85d4e5095a94bb188fb95a57d20b11e1","tid":1322723,"uid":50658,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:35:39.000Z","msg":"五個"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:36:48.000Z","msg":"第四同第五個 真兄弟就會明白"},{"pid":"8f3dfbd11a0eded9e500acba285e64b70db38ac3","tid":1322723,"uid":188310,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:37:03.000Z","msg":"又試水溫?"},{"pid":"5ef4a4329382fd71b04305b669604629987f1ca0","tid":1322723,"uid":202621,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:38:26.000Z","msg":"睇完即刻原諒了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96fd8f7f230c8c56ebe292e7a822a44c2a4fbfe2","tid":1322723,"uid":256246,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"